track_notes: This track is a detour off the Bronte Way - a walk from Burnley to Bradford which I did in 2008.  I detoured to activate Boulsworth Hill. There is room to park at SD 906352.
track_title: Track leading off the Bronte Way

track_notes:
Little scope for parking at track start. Parking spot 1.2 km down-hill to the SE.

Straightforward route. Nothing tricky except maybe Hey Slacks Clough when in spate.
